sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Host as ChuTri
actor Member as ThanhVien
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant VoiceSvc as VoiceService
participant MeetDb as Mongo_Meeting
participant SFU as Mediasoup

Note over Host,SFU: Chặng 2 - Ngoại lệ join/end
Member->>Gateway: Yêu cầu join meeting
Gateway->>VoiceSvc: Validate meeting + quyền
alt Meeting đã kết thúc
  VoiceSvc-->>Member: Từ chối join
else Không đủ quyền
  VoiceSvc-->>Member: 403
else Hợp lệ
  VoiceSvc->>SFU: Cấp transport
  SFU-->>Member: Join success
end
Host->>Gateway: POST /api/meetings/:id/end
VoiceSvc->>MeetDb: Set ended
VoiceSvc->>SFU: Close room
